{"tid":2068754,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【白色恐怖】畢業班相被P圖 學生抗爭手勢「五一」竟變「四二」","createTime":"2020-06-18T02:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T03:54:57.000Z","uid":213952,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4678acbd5051c47f6b594085f9e4c3f71494bcb4","tid":2068754,"uid":213952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T02:14:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/breaking/20200618/DU7HSHCY3VIHW4SRLESFNRTQ5A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200618%2FDU7HSHCY3VIHW4SRLESFNRTQ5A%2F&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=4c891e97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200618%2FDU7HSHCY3VIHW4SRLESFNRTQ5A%2F&h=234402ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/breaking/20200618/DU7HSHCY3VIHW4SRLESFNRTQ5A/</a><br />\n<br />\n教育界近日濔漫白色恐怖，中學畢業生就連在畢業照中做手勢支持「五大訴求」竟也被打壓。《蘋果》收到一群來自中華傳道會李賢堯紀念中學的畢業生投訴，指控有攝影師擅自修改畢業大合照，打壓學生言論自由。因不少學生拍畢業照時舉起寓意「五大訴求，缺一不可」的「五一」手勢，但攝影師曬相後竟「P圖」，至少把5名學生的「五一」手勢竄改成「四二」手勢，令五大訴求「消失」。有家長後來幾番追究攝影師及取回原圖，卻不得要領，對方更辯稱改圖「是學校的指示」，家長不禁批評學界失自由，「連一個手勢都容納唔到！」"},{"pid":"9f807b4e773d59b044e3d26740d2c28b81195e69","tid":2068754,"uid":204356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T02:15:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e621e6793de222168ba84198c4b9d4d441f10b0","tid":2068754,"uid":203889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:51:42.000Z","msg":"下咁都得"},{"pid":"d551274d48c0c83b358191513fdbb5e4cca8fe01","tid":2068754,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:53:24.000Z","msg":"咁撚肉酸"},{"pid":"b19994ce194cb92444905141ce9d557eb2c98bc7","tid":2068754,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislik